summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2341 for the improvement of the Alley in Block Eight (8) of Randell's Addition to The City of Seattle, from East Union Street to East Spring Street and between Thirty-sixth Avenue and Thirty-seventh Avenue, all in The City of Seattle, by grading the same; under Ordinance No. 24339, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
